## Playwright iframe 处理

本 skill 同时提供 Playwright 脚本示例，展示如何处理复杂的 iframe 场景。

### 脚本位置

`scripts/playwright_iframe_demo.py` - 完整的 iframe 操作示例

### 核心 API 对比

| 功能 | CDP (本 skill) | Playwright |
|------|---------------|------------|
| 获取 frame 树 | `Page.getFrameTree` | `page.main_frame` + `frame.child_frames` |
| 进入 iframe | 手动切换 context | `page.frame_locator(selector)` |
| 操作 iframe 元素 | `Runtime.evaluate` 在目标 frame | `frame_locator.locator().click()` |
| 跨域处理 | 需创建独立 session | 自动处理 |

### Playwright 处理 iframe 示例

```python
from playwright.async_api import async_playwright

async def handle_iframe():
    async with async_playwright() as p:
        browser = await p.chromium.launch()
        page = await browser.new_page()
        await page.goto("https://mail.163.com")
        
        # 方式1: 遍历 frame 树
        def dump_frames(frame, indent=""):
            print(f"{indent}{frame.name or 'unnamed'}: {frame.url}")
            for child in frame.child_frames:
                dump_frames(child, indent + "  ")
        
        dump_frames(page.main_frame)
        
        # 方式2: 使用 frame_locator 进入 iframe
        login_frame = page.frame_locator('iframe[id^="x-URS-iframe"]')
        
        # 在 iframe 内操作元素
        email_input = login_frame.locator('input[placeholder*="邮箱"]')
        await email_input.fill("your_email@163.com")
        
        await browser.close()
```

### 运行示例脚本

```bash
# 安装依赖
pip3 install playwright
playwright install chromium

# 运行示例
cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/headed-browser-open-v3
python3 scripts/playwright_iframe_demo.py
```

### 163 邮箱 iframe 结构参考

```
https://mail.163.com/ (主页面)
├── iframe: frameforlogin (about:blank) - 空
├── iframe: frameJS6 (preload6.htm) - 预加载
└── iframe: x-URS-iframe... (dl.reg.163.com) - ⭐登录表单
```

**注意**: 登录表单在跨域 iframe 中 (dl.reg.163.com)，Playwright 的 `frame_locator` 可以无缝处理这种情况。

